{"title":"Veronica’s Custom Painted Specialized Aethos – Spencer Harding","link":"https://theradavist.com/veronicas-custom-painted-specialized-aethos/","date":1714917617000,"content":"<p><em>Down in Tucson, AZ Spencer met up with local artist and mechanic John “Cookie” Sands to photograph the bike he custom-painted for his partner Veronica. It started as a <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/specialized-aethos-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized Aethos</a> but after it got a few paint chips, Cookie decided to give the bike a truly one-of-a-kind custom paint job. Make sure to check out the gallery of all the hand-painted details…</em></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"887\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-34.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-34.jpg?w=887&amp;quality=75 887w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-34.jpg?resize=768,1154&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-33.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>You may recognize <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cookieballs/\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie</a> from Josh’s amazing cover image from this year’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/single-speed-arizona-2024-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\">SSAZ</a> coverage, jumping over the campfire. He’s quite the shreddy bike rider but he is an equally talented <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cookiesartpage/\" target=\"_blank\">artist</a>. When his partner, Veronica, kept asking him to paint her Aethos little did she know how far he would go…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image0.jpeg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image0.jpeg?w=960&amp;quality=75 960w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image0.jpeg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1913\" height=\"2856\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?fit=1200,2856&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?w=1913&amp;quality=75 1913w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?resize=1200,1792&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?resize=768,1147&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?resize=1029,1536&amp;quality=75 1029w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/image1.jpeg?resize=1372,2048&amp;quality=75 1372w\" /></p>\n<p>With over two hundred hours spent painting the frame, after work and before bed for weeks, the paint was truly a labor of love. The base coat was painted with <a href=\"https://spraybike.us/\" target=\"_blank\">Spray Bike</a> which Cookie then spent many hours meticulously drawing each line with paint pens. Finishing off the paint was a sparkle clear coat for that extra bit of shine. The style appears to be a nod to post-impressionism.  An iconic saguaro and of course “S-Works” break up the continual flurry of lines and swirls that cover the frame.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-5.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2004\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?w=2004&amp;quality=75 2004w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-17.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-20.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3>Spec:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frame:Specialized S-Works Aethos</li>\n<li>Stem: S-Works</li>\n<li>Bars: S-Works</li>\n<li>Cranks: Force AXS power meter</li>\n<li>Cassette: Sram Red</li>\n<li>Brakes: Sram Force</li>\n<li>Wheelset: Roval Terra CL</li>\n<li>Tires: S-Works Turbo 700×28</li>\n<li>Seatpost: Roval Alpinist Carbon</li>\n<li>Saddle: Specialized Power</li>\n<li>Rear Derailleur: Sram Force</li>\n<li>Front Derailleur: Sram Force</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-31.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2004\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?w=2004&amp;quality=75 2004w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-14.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2004\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?w=2004&amp;quality=75 2004w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-24.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This bike is sure to be the envy of anyone riding up Mt Lemmon or out on the bike path around Tucson. While a stock Aethos might not look nearly as striking if you are in the market for one don’t miss John’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/specialized-aethos-review/\">Review</a> from a few years back if you need some extra light goodness in your stable.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2004\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?w=2004&amp;quality=75 2004w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/04/Veronicas-Custom-Painted-Aethos-32-1.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>All that work didn’t deter his spirit and Cookie is working on painting his personal bike at the moment in the same incredible detail.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/veronicas-custom-painted-specialized-aethos/\">Veronica’s Custom Painted Specialized Aethos</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"fde1397a3a87173b30dca6bfc9197e75236aa993409ecc58598037daad306150","category":"Cycling"}